<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>923</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dāng zāi nán bù duàn de chū xiàn, de shàng yòu yǒu le zhàn huǒ.
 wǒ men bù néng bù shuō, bù néng bù bǎ fú yīn chuán bō.
 rén xīn huāng huāng bù ān, wēn yì lái le wú chù duǒ.
 shén de ér nǚ dāng tǐng shēn ér chū, gāo hǎn zhǔ shì bì nán suǒ.
 wǒ de qīn rén nǎ wǒ de zǔ guó,
 jīn rì shì guī qī, yào chuán biàn wàn guó.
 yé hé huá fā nù de rì zi, liè guó dōu dān dāng bù qǐ.
 xiàn zài shì huǐ gǎi de shí kè, zài bù yào cuò guò.</lyrics>
<title>dāng zāi nán bù duàn de chū xiàn 迦南923</title>
</song>